%section.page-title-wrapper
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-6.page-title
        %h4 About
      .col-xs-6.hidden-xs.breadcrumb-wrapper
        %ol.breadcrumb.pull-right
          %li
            = link_to 'Home', root_path
          %li.active About

%section
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-6
        %h5.subpage-title RailsCasts Tips
        %p.justified
          Many Rails developers have learned something from Ryan Bates through his RailsCasts, but one screencast tends to deliver more knowledge than described in the title. This project is looking to point forward this extra knowledge. Also, its a way of saying
          %b "Thank you Ryan".
        %p.justified In fact, many of the features in this site implements tips and knowledge taken from RailsCasts.
      .col-md-6.wrapper-1
        = image_tag 'railscasts_logo.png', alt: 'RailsCasts'
        %hr
        %p.justified
          All RailsCasts related material (including videos and image files) belong to
          = link_to 'railscasts.com', 'http://railscasts.com'
          an it's producers.

